  "3299920": {
    "name": "Liminal Point",
    "steam_appid": 3299920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/72892b88afd52d336d888fd3f10fb5ae.avif?t=1765981145\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras_big/72892b88afd52d336d888fd3f10fb5ae.avif?t=1765981145 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liminal Point是一款致敬经典的心理生存恐怖游戏，同时带来现代且令人毛骨悚然的体验，模糊了现实与噩梦之间的界限。游戏背景设定在一座神秘、荒凉且雾气笼罩的岛屿上，你将扮演曾是一颗摇滚新星的莉拉，揭开她乐队成员米拉失踪背后的诡异真相，以及岛上隐藏的险恶秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着莉拉探索岛上阴森恐怖、被遗弃的地点，她将遇到神秘的信息、令人费解的扭曲生物，以及一段不愿被埋藏的阴森往事。每一步都让周围的世界变得更加超现实，挑战着她对现实的把握，迫使她直面自己内心深处的恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否揭开真相，还是会让这座岛屿将你变为下一个牺牲品？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经典生存恐怖游戏</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现代手法演绎该类型游戏永恒的经典公式：有限的资源、紧张的遭遇战以及令人胆寒的氛围。谨慎管理你有限的背包空间，依靠地图明智地规划下一步行动，在雾气缭绕的岛屿、宅邸、医院或下水道间穿梭。生存悬于一线，每个决定都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/6555ab12d08e7b35c93ea5a60ac8f5e3.poster.avif?t=1765981145\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/6555ab12d08e7b35c93ea5a60ac8f5e3.webm?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/6555ab12d08e7b35c93ea5a60ac8f5e3.mp4?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式心理恐怖</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你拼凑莉拉的过去以及米拉在事件中所扮演的角色，你将揭开一个关于悲剧、记忆以及现实与噩梦界限模糊的层次丰富的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/5b30e9fd5ba3217247b9f0ec2274d682.poster.avif?t=1765981145\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/5b30e9fd5ba3217247b9f0ec2274d682.webm?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/5b30e9fd5ba3217247b9f0ec2274d682.mp4?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>氛围探索</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于阴森恐怖的地点，从摇摇欲坠的宅邸到雾气笼罩的街道，每个角落都隐藏着新的谜团——或是危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/ec8bafaff0d163c378003608ac89d001.poster.avif?t=1765981145\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/ec8bafaff0d163c378003608ac89d001.webm?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/ec8bafaff0d163c378003608ac89d001.mp4?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富视觉体验</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用独特的等距视角，结合细致入微的环境和动态光影，让Liminal Point的世界栩栩如生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/9938f6eef38752b3168ec3043184afa5.poster.avif?t=1765981145\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/9938f6eef38752b3168ec3043184afa5.webm?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/9938f6eef38752b3168ec3043184afa5.mp4?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜的音效设计</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人胆寒的原创配乐和环境音效将你沉浸于岛屿荒凉大厅、废弃宅邸等场景的紧张氛围中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/a2b4ef09d35acb7b7e4000efb453a858.poster.avif?t=1765981145\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/a2b4ef09d35acb7b7e4000efb453a858.webm?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299920/extras/a2b4ef09d35acb7b7e4000efb453a858.mp4?t=1765981145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备揭开Liminal Point的秘密吧。但请记住：真相是有代价的。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 日语, 俄语, 简体中文, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 意大利语, 土耳其语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
